<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Table Occupied</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>body { background-color: #07090F; color: #ffffff; }</style>
</head>
<body class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-6 text-center">
    <div class="bg-[#121624] border border-white/10 p-8 rounded-3xl max-w-sm shadow-2xl">
        <div class="text-6xl mb-4">✋</div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Table <%= tableNumber %> is Occupied</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Someone is currently ordering or eating at this table at <%= shopName %>. Please wait until they finish or ask staff for a different table.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>